{"tid":185874,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"香港唯二有資格擁有紋章既大學 HKU CUHK","createTime":"2017-04-03T18:36:07.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-04T02:51:42.000Z","uid":14170,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"5dd50d8ec1e96d3b7956e5adc68d5a6a9a9b2105","tid":185874,"uid":14170,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-03T18:36:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/04/04/023606_a1d64566369e0cefcdee43e9b4903e4d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F04%2F04%2F023606_a1d64566369e0cefcdee43e9b4903e4d.jpg&h=dc14ed21&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d6584146198ac2e1312ee74fd04dc9571091bd8a","tid":185874,"uid":14170,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-03T18:36:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/04/04/023643_b71853fcb07b32d88979bfbabc8bfbbd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F04%2F04%2F023643_b71853fcb07b32d88979bfbabc8bfbbd.jpg&h=dbd7bf38&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"6916c98f30484b6ec51c47f7cd1f44eb52aeb610","tid":185874,"uid":37525,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-03T18:47:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />有無人紋身會紋呢啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n都係公仔啫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n都有龍呀虎呀咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9081dc2a4bcd0ea81ea0da334e773af99e9b844b","tid":185874,"uid":79627,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-03T18:50:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />有無人紋身會紋呢啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n都係公仔啫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n都有龍呀虎呀咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n紋章啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"66d3b08d42411373bb7d4b812860337e6a608841","tid":185874,"uid":14170,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-03T18:51:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />有無人紋身會紋呢啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n都係公仔啫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n都有龍呀虎呀咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n紋章啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nChing 係咪唔知咩叫紋章 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n代表文化歷史地位"},{"pid":"2492fc0e181733b8eaa078b2af1453902711470f","tid":185874,"uid":14170,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-03T18:58:22.000Z","msg":"所謂紋章 coat of arms，是中世紀歐洲皇權貴族的產物，用於盾徽、袍徽，以識別比武場中被頭盔蒙着面孔的武士，漸漸變成一種世襲封賜。到了近代，英國的紋章院 College of Arms 便專門審批這些具貴族傳統的＂皇家御准印鑑＂，以彰顯承先啟後、世代相傳的機構團體。<br />\n<br />\n港大創校於1911 年，據載到了1913 年才有校徽和校訓。盾形的徽章頂部是一隻英國味甚濃的雄獅，坐鎮着校訓＂明德格物＂和＂sapientia et virtus＂（智慧與德行 - 拉丁文）。至於皇家御准的港大紋章則複雜很多，盾形徽章的兩側，有一龍一獅，集中西之大成，寓意至為明顯。所以，有關港大的網上資料（包括互動百科） 一直以來都說：大學興辦者的期望，是將港大發展成中西合璧的學府。這說法合情合理，至今不悖。<br />\n<br />\n然而，自2011 年港大百年慶典上李克強說過中央特設專款資助港大，稱港大是 「為中國而設」 之後，不少網頁都將史實竄改，說法有歪情理： 「英國政府和其他香港英資公司如匯豐銀行的資助下，盧押最終籌得足夠資金組建大學，並於1910年3月16日主持大學的動工儀式，主張港大『為中國而立』。」這些網頁除了內地的百度百科等，還包括維基百科。<br />\n<br />\n文字隨時可以改，圖徽設計已成定案，塗改不易，但有心人可以避重就輕。不過，設計港大百周年紀念郵票首日封的那位仁兄，不知是太尊重史實傳統還是太大意了，竟然將獅龍紋章和雄獅坐鎮的校徽大剌剌的放上去。<br />\n<br />\n港大的校旗是綠色，傳統顏色也是綠色。2008 年及以前的榮譽學位頒授典禮的禮臺佈置都是綠色，之後有過紅綠滲雜，近年已全面赤化。（參考港大專頁 congregation gallery）。<br />\n<br />\n七十年代港大陸佑堂的鐘樓頂每天都掛着綠色的明德格物校旗，除非打風落雨，否則它一定傲然飄揚，直至下午六時才卸下，不須根據甚麼禮儀守則，已成了日日如是的港大傳統。回歸之後不知何時開始，陸佑堂再不見校旗蹤影。2013 年 3 月 16 日港大奠基日，朋友發來一幀照片，鐘樓頂沒有綠旗，代之以五星紅旗。象徵學術尊嚴的港大校旗，竟然屈辱地掛在西面小塔樓。這是對港大傳統精神蓄意矮化、篾視，港大師生有幾多人留意？<br />\n<br />\n如果有一天，全新班子的校委會以「與時並進」為理由，提出以下三點修改港大校旗，大家不必驚訝：<br />\n<br />\n1. 獅改為龍；<br />\n2. sapientia et virtus 改為 ming de ge wu / m&iacute;ng d&eacute; g&eacute; w&ugrave;；<br />\n3. 綠色改為紅色。<br />\n<br />\n要好好守護港大紋章 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"271a662bfdf2652319f9cd913a80e6c9325cbda0","tid":185874,"uid":39253,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-03T18:59:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/zh/thumb/7/72/Hong_Kong_Shue_Yan_University_logo.svg/325px-Hong_Kong_Shue_Yan_University_logo.svg.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fzh%2Fthumb%2F7%2F72%2FHong_Kong_Shue_Yan_University_logo.svg%2F325px-Hong_Kong_Shue_Yan_University_logo.svg.png&h=ce1078dd&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d3573122048b5762a7a47a1eb97d100ccd98c6b3","tid":185874,"uid":7294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-03T19:02:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/zh/thumb/7/72/Hong_Kong_Shue_Yan_University_logo.svg/325px-Hong_Kong_Shue_Yan_University_logo.svg.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fzh%2Fthumb%2F7%2F72%2FHong_Kong_Shue_Yan_University_logo.svg%2F325px-Hong_Kong_Shue_Yan_University_logo.svg.png&h=ce1078dd&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n秒"},{"pid":"5896782c86e971aec760a0a85e4db3a3e4658435","tid":185874,"uid":12709,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-03T19:03:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/V9em4uJ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FV9em4uJ.jpg&h=425b69ee&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/X4QBL7G.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FX4QBL7G.jpg&h=4258d146&s={SIZE