kquote><br />\n秒</blockquote><br />\n新細明體"},{"pid":"e6a6778ab06588b19a9fa1ca244a067fd9032558","tid":185874,"uid":13385,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-03T19:08:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/zh/thumb/7/72/Hong_Kong_Shue_Yan_University_logo.svg/325px-Hong_Kong_Shue_Yan_University_logo.svg.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fzh%2Fthumb%2F7%2F72%2FHong_Kong_Shue_Yan_University_logo.svg%2F325px-Hong_Kong_Shue_Yan_University_logo.svg.png&h=ce1078dd&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n秒</blockquote><br />\n新細明體</blockquote><br />\n小畫家"},{"pid":"e65246c4a6b4813fde2efad937b0569eb45b47e9","tid":185874,"uid":988,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-03T19:09:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/zh/thumb/7/72/Hong_Kong_Shue_Yan_University_logo.svg/325px-Hong_Kong_Shue_Yan_University_logo.svg.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fzh%2Fthumb%2F7%2F72%2FHong_Kong_Shue_Yan_University_logo.svg%2F325px-Hong_Kong_Shue_Yan_University_logo.svg.png&h=ce1078dd&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n秒</blockquote><br />\n新細明體</blockquote><br />\n真係好撚樣衰.."},{"pid":"4bc315101927ecbdcea600a73fa4c1b3bab14688","tid":185874,"uid":37197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-03T19:11:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/zh/thumb/7/72/Hong_Kong_Shue_Yan_University_logo.svg/325px-Hong_Kong_Shue_Yan_University_logo.svg.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fzh%2Fthumb%2F7%2F72%2FHong_Kong_Shue_Yan_University_logo.svg%2F325px-Hong_Kong_Shue_Yan_University_logo.svg.png&h=ce1078dd&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n秒</blockquote><br />\n新細明體</blockquote><br />\n真係好撚樣衰..</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />好撚柒"},{"pid":"cfa645f08eb5428f06dcca8b2867ab35ebe82bab","tid":185874,"uid":33825,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-03T19:12:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/zh/thumb/7/72/Hong_Kong_Shue_Yan_University_logo.svg/325px-Hong_Kong_Shue_Yan_University_logo.svg.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fzh%2Fthumb%2F7%2F72%2FHong_Kong_Shue_Yan_University_logo.svg%2F325px-Hong_Kong_Shue_Yan_University_logo.svg.png&h=ce1078dd&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n秒</blockquote><br />\n新細明體</blockquote><br />\n真係好撚樣衰..</blockquote><br />\n打大佬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"beee4ed5220b8f1d352fb81609fcc3cb4e8ed457","tid":185874,"uid":51978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-03T19:13:37.000Z","msg":"和香港大學不同，中大雖然是香港第一所正式獲得完整紋章的大學，但是一般卻是通常使用簡易版本的校徽，以體現中大追尋樸實的文化作風。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nbtw<br />\n<br />\n底下個箇四隻字係乜？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有無人知？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c7958c0060d29ed943366f977ac2a88c57277436","tid":185874,"uid":36383,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-03T19:15:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/zh/thumb/7/72/Hong_Kong_Shue_Yan_University_logo.svg/325px-Hong_Kong_Shue_Yan_University_logo.svg.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fzh%2Fthumb%2F7%2F72%2FHong_Kong_Shue_Yan_University_logo.svg%2F325px-Hong_Kong_Shue_Yan_University_logo.svg.png&h=ce1078dd&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n秒</blockquote><br />\n新細明體</blockquote><br />\n真係好撚樣衰..</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 小畫家都畫得好過佢"},{"pid":"ecdb38d67c5d818f6b8a3c868a41bdae617fbb17","tid":185874,"uid":51978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-03T19:17:30.000Z","msg":"香港中文大學成立後，校董會按大學條例經校長代表向英國倫敦的英國紋章院（College of Arms）申請授予紋章。<br />\n<br />\n紋章院於1967年授予中大紋章，是香港第一所正式獲得完整紋章的大學。<br />\n<br />\n香港中文大學是香港兩間具有紋章的大學之一（1967年獲得紋章的香港中文大學、1981年獲得紋章的香港大學）。<br />\n<br />\n在1981年，香港大學建校70週年時，大學向紋章院申請一個完整的紋章，此前只擁有盾章的香港大學，終於添加了部分包括冠頂及扶持盾牌的獸形，此項申請於1984年獲英國紋章院批准，成為擁有完整紋章的大學，顯示出大學歷史悠久的一面。紋章以香港盾徽為藍圖繪劃。居頂的是代表英格蘭的小獅子。左面是代表中國的龍，右面是代表英國的獅子，腳踏着的草地代表香港島。三頭生物都繫着翡翠項飾。頭盔與綵帶代表勇敢的騎士。<br />\n<br />\nbtw 呢個網係咪誤導 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"http://100.hku.hk/download/hku_booklet_final.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F100.hku.hk%2Fdownload%2Fhku_booklet_final.pdf&d=aEshCX%2BOVPgV%2F8nDcbq7VwHuyxefasl%2FZxVLfhQSBMM%3D&h=d5d49057\" target=\"_blank\">http://100.hku.hk/download/hku_booklet_final.pdf</a><br />\n佢話港大係本地唯一擁有紋章嘅大學 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"402ce5e4cb1041ebf514c01629aefd89f4415d10","tid":185874,"uid":92376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-03T19:18:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/zh/thumb/7/72/Hong_Kong_Shue_Yan_University_logo.svg/325px-Hong_Kong_Shue_Yan_University_logo.svg.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fzh%2Fthumb%2F7%2F72%2FHong_Kong_Shue_Yan_University_logo.svg%2F325px-Hong_Kong_Shue_Yan_University_logo.svg.png&h=ce1078dd&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n秒</blockquote><br />\n新細明體</blockquote><br />\n真係好撚樣衰..</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 小畫家都畫得好過佢</blockquote><br />\n佢綠色果part咩事，小木偶講大話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5cff35335ce42cfa9316d3c02b099206b3f653c7","tid":185874,"uid":92376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-03T19:22:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>和香港大學不同，中大雖然是香港第一所正式獲得完整紋章的大學，但是一般卻是通常使用簡易版本的校徽，以體現中大追尋樸實的文化作風。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nbtw<br />\n<br />\n底下個箇四隻字係乜？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有無人知？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n利約安計?"},{"pid":"6c196e9c2cf8b7129d7ee5ca25fe79f491b01d15","tid":185874,"uid":88813,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-03T19:23:24.000Z","msg":"博文約禮"},{"pid":"32ac2c84fd78188879b8ac9a1b2f143cca4d2280","tid":185874,"uid":51978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-03T19:24:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>博文約禮</blockquote><br />\nthx <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n啱啱查校訓都如夢初醒 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5fe94d969762dd3ab399e36dfe421e82534a1956","tid":185874,"uid":9394,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-03T19:26:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>和香港大學不同，中大雖然是香港第一所正式獲得完整紋章的大學，但是一般卻是通常使用簡易版本的校徽，以體現中大追尋樸實的文化作風。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nbtw<br />\n<br />\n底下個箇四隻字係乜？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" cla